steps.html_instructions: Head west on E University Ave toward Filmore St
Merge onto I-235 E via the ramp on the left to E 14th St/E 15th St

Keep right at the fork to stay on Exit 137A, follow signs for I-80 E/Davenport and merge onto I-80 E
Entering Illinois
Take the I-55 S/I-74 E exit toward St Louis/Indianapolis

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-74/US-51 S, follow signs for Interstate 74 E/Indianapolis/Decatur
Continue to follow I-74
Entering Indiana
Take exit 73 for Interstate 465 N toward U.S. 136 W/Crawfordsville Road
Keep left, follow signs for U.S. 136 W/Crawfordsville Rd

Turn left onto US-136 E/Crawfordsville Rd
Continue to follow Crawfordsville Rd
At the traffic circle, take the 2nd exit onto W 16th St
